## How the Backtracking Works

For any cell `dp[i][j]`, the optimal split `k` is the one that **satisfies this equation exactly:**
```
dp[i][k] + dp[k+1][j] + dims[i-1] * dims[k] * dims[j]  ==  dp[i][j]
